      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:2:13:1",
      "text": [
        " الْكَادُّ عَلَى عِيَالِهِ كَالْمُجَاهِدِ فِي سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hammad Bin Usman, from Al Halby, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The toiler upon his family is like the combatant in the Way of Allah<sup>azwj</sup>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hammad ibn ‘Uthman from af-Halabiy who has said the following: “Abu ‘ Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘A person working hard for his family is like Mujahid (fighter) for the cause of Allah. ’” "
        ]
      }
